{
  "stem": "8072.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that was a good sight.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was May 1, 1945.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that day, you know, myself, for some reason, I wasn't as weak as some of, you know, some of the rest of the prisoners.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For some reason, I had some strength.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we were liberated, we were just-- went wild, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I remember just going in-- some of the houses, they were empty, because even the German people, they were running away or something.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It could be maybe the SS lived around there, and they were running away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I remember going in a house, and it was empty, and to take a shower.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think I remember I took a shower.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I took-- and I found some clothes in there and changed clothes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember whether I had any food or not, but I remember taking a shower and changing clothes.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, and then when-- and then we-- then we lived on a farm, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because some of the guys, the prisoners, they rode with some American-- the American military police with some of the army, you know, to try to find the Gestapo, or the SS, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember an incident that this one-- they found this one SS man, and the-- and the, the-- besides the American army.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The one guy that was with the American Army at that time, he was, he was also a Jewish prisoner, but I think he was going-- he was under a Polish name, an assumed Polish name.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
